Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:09.68,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,As always, I can't make any sense of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:11.21,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:12.57,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You better get ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:13.76,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.25,0:00:16.68,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,And you're as icy as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:17.78,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:19.20,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You really piss me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:21.25,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:23.63,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Give us the start signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:25.96,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:27.75,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll race 100 meters,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:29.84,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,freestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.18,0:00:32.16,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:33.88,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:39.38,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Rin-chan has a stronger kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:40.01,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.89,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru's stroke is faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:25.99,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Gou?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:29.25,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:32.00,Text,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,From: Matsuoka Gou\NSubject:\NDid you get to see Nanase-san and the other guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:36.21,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that \NI can't ever beat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:52.43,EpTitle,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(529,467)}Memories in the Distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:49.49,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:52.09,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Do you actually feel bad \Nabout what you've done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:53.28,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:55.99,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,First you trespass in \Nan abandoned building,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:02:57.86,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,now you trespass in \Nanother school's pool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.70,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, we're fortunate that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:03.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,they've agreed not to \Nmake a big deal of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:07.28,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. I think that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:09.91,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,There's a famous saying that \Napplies to this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:13.54,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,In Ancient China during the Shang Dynasty,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Duke Tai of Qi would fish without any bait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:16.67,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I hate fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:18.67,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:22.26,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ama-chan wasn't much help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:25.01,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how that fish saying goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.22,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru, do you know...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:27.55,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:29.39,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:31.40,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:33.47,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Gou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:35.82,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to call me Kou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:36.88,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Does it really matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.40,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,It matters! I'm Kou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:39.92,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Gou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:40.85,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Kou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:41.68,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Gou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:42.99,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Kou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:43.72,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Kou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:44.37,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Gou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.33,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.91,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,So were you able to see my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.10,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:53.83,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan's so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.34,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't seen each \Nother in four years!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:59.02,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,And the first thing he does is \Nchallenge Haru-chan to a race.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:02.18,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,He completely ignored me and Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.30,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't get a chance \Nto talk about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:07.62,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard anything \Nfrom Rin, Kou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:11.72,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I've sent him e-mails and called \Nhis cell without any luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:13.89,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I even called his dorm number \Nand nobody picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:17.00,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,How come Rin-chan's changed so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:19.08,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen in Australia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.23,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:24.89,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping that he'd open \Nup after meeting you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:29.95,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you responsible for Rin \Nshowing up at the swimming club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.49,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say that I was responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.67,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I was just trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.50,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I happened to overhear your conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.50,Text 2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard that they're tearing down \Nthe swimming club you used to go to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.50,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,so I sent him a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:43.77,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,But he never replied.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:46.38,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you went to \NHaru's place yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.71,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was hoping he \Nmight have some answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:51.18,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I have a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.31,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start a swim club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:56.85,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can see Rin-chan at tournaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:59.98,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'm not sure Haru will \Nbe on board with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.98,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Knock yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:02.66,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:03.81,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:05.03,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.59,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We're good to go then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.82,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.03,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:12.45,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be doing this by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.71,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You're expected to join the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.12,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.69,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:24.38,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Girls my age shouldn't ogle naked men!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.63,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Must... not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.38,Nar/Thought/Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,look...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:29.14,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:31.60,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,incredible triceps!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:36.88,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Haru-chan wasn't \Nwith us the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:38.89,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,This is Rin-chan's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:42.93,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello. It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:43.69,Main,Haruka,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuoka
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:45.94,Main,Haruka,0000,0000,0000,,Kou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:48.57,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.22,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about what my \Nbrother did yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.08,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:55.48,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if you're making tea, I \Nhave some squid to go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.69,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wouldn't chocolate be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.30,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,We'll compromise and have mackerel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.37,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:02.63,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.16,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.49,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:07.79,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:10.59,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That's the trophy the \Nfour of us won as kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:13.22,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Rin told us that he no longer needed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.23,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:20.05,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Haru's the sole \Nexception in this photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:23.39,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan is always smiling on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:26.48,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,You make him sound like a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:32.63,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so is this the first time Rin's \Ncome back to Japan since he left?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:33.38,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:35.91,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,He came back every year for New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.56,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.87,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,And he never told us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.13,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:43.85,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.71,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Since everyone's on board,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:49.51,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I picked up a new club application form.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.44,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You move fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:54.26,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's important to get the ball rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.69,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, the purpose of this club is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:58.94,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,to train our minds and \Nbodies through swimming
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:01.24,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,and improve the school experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:03.07,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,And you know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:05.47,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,There will be three members initially.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:07.44,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Mako-chan, you can be the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:09.82,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, shouldn't it be Haru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.15,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,He's the fastest swimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:12.93,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't about speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.10,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Different people are better \Nat different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.71,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:20.50,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,First-years are on cleanup duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.50,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Second-years are in \Ncharge of the chlorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:25.80,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Third-years have a meeting once \Nthey've finished stretching!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.92,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, Captain Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.09,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.22,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,That means Mako-chan is the captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:34.84,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,and Haru-chan can be the vice-captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.22,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't just volunteer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.76,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:42.08,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Vice-captain is just an empty title \Nwith no actual responsibilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:42.91,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:46.77,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You just offended every \Nvice-captain on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.09,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the treasurer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:50.87,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,which means we just need a faculty advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.01,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:55.23,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about asking Ama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.78,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ama-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:08:00.16,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a crazy story from \None of our classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.41,Faculty,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Faculty Office
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:01.41,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:03.41,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:05.15,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Sports aren't my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.58,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I teach classical literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.47,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:12.30,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,until last year, you had a job in \NTokyo that involved swimsuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.48,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:14.69,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Not so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:15.98,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:18.14,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It was Nashimoto-kun, from our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:22.94,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Did you work for a swimsuit designer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:23.83,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.60,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, you could say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.77,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:30.44,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,we would be thrilled to have you\N advise us about the technology
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:31.89,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,that goes into competitive swimwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:33.32,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Advise us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.25,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.73,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,If you really need me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:39.94,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:41.34,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.37,samezuka,,0000,0000,0000,,Samezuka Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:46.35,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Matsuoka Rin's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:48.26,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to see my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:53.50,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, looks like Matsuoka-kun isn't back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:54.88,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:00.78,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.18,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:05.14,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Totally a prestigious school's swimming club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.06,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Traps and pecs everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.86,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,They're gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.57,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so it's you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:14.64,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,The one who's looking for her big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:15.94,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.03,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:19.64,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:21.62,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:27.45,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I'm looking for \NMatsuoka Rin, my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:28.83,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:32.09,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,There's nobody named \NMatsuoka on the swim team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.31,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:55.94,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:58.86,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,in regard to the swim club \Ncharter that you submitted...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:03.03,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,After strict review by the faculty,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:07.09,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,it was approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.05,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:10.96,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! I knew we could count on \Na former swimwear company employee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.42,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:15.40,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I can do when \NI put my mind to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:18.77,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,However, a school organization is \Nrequired to have four members,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:20.64,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,so you'll have to find one more person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:24.47,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,And there's one more condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.35,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.82,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.48,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so much nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:33.29,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:36.51,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you must restore this \Npool to a usable state.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.19,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You're not allowed to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:43.39,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were willing to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.99,Flyer,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Let's swim together\NIwatobi Swim Club
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:31.58,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:34.32,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.03,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,It's cleaned up rather nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:49.39,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you get out of that \Nchair and give us a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:50.81,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:53.81,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,The UV rays this time of year are brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:56.15,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,You're still young, \Nso it's not an issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:58.46,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:00.82,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like we're back in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.48,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Grade schoolers wouldn't \Nbe asked to fix a pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:05.91,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:08.37,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's all cleaned up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:11.04,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Are you here to help, Gou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:12.90,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to call me Kou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.38,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you don't get any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:16.38,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What? You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:29.69,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:31.18,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Interested in joining the swim club?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.81,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I've already decided to \Njoin the track team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:34.88,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:37.13,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun swimming together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:38.61,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you want to swim in a pool
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:41.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,when the ocean's right over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.95,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,If you join now, you'll receive
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:48.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,a year's supply of Iwatobi's \Nmascot character, Iwatobi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:49.70,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.25,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,No luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.86,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody wants to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:57.00,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting to look like we \Nfixed the pool for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.13,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.18,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to use our last resort...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.60,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We have Ama-chan give the \Nshirt off her back for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:08.43,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.57,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Advertise the fact that \NAma-chan is our advisor,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:12.77,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,and tell everyone they'll get
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,to see her in a swimsuit if they join!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:17.01,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's giving up her shirt, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:21.40,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.53,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, I'll quit immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:29.27,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,I swore to myself that I'd \Nnever put on a swimsuit again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.16,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:31.71,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Are we clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:32.84,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:36.80,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the juice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:37.62,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.81,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't quite get it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.11,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Get what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:45.54,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you try to start a swim \Nclub when you were first-years?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:49.06,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru wasn't interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:51.02,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,But he's such a good swimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:54.34,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru joined the swim \Nclub in middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:58.29,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,but he quit at the end of our first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.61,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.04,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:03.09,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't want to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:06.05,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Our old swimming club was shut \Ndown around the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.32,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,and Haru hasn't done any \Ncompetitive swimming since.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:13.74,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,So he wanted to quit swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:15.66,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.46,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if my brother's the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:19.51,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:21.51,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for my brother the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:23.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and found out he's not on the swim team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.67,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,He transferred to Samezuka Academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:28.05,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,but he didn't join the swim team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.63,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:32.10,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he just raced Haru and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.95,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,He must have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:38.61,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he's given up on swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:40.27,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,No, that can't be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.19,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, when they raced that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.20,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.22,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:54.52,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,He lost ground to Rin-chan on every turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:56.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's nearly caught up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:15:00.42,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I can't shake him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:02.29,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,They're making the final turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.10,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Who hit first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:05.21,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Too close to tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.13,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,They're neck and neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:11.13,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,No, Rin's legs put him \Nahead after the turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.05,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Haru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.28,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.78,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,This sensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:37.29,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.79,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:44.34,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,No need to rely on or \Nwork with other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:49.59,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to drift through \Nthe water alone in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:52.26,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:52.26,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:55.72,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:58.47,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.85,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,My brother won?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:04.10,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, didn't Rin tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:09.07,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't respond, so I thought \Nhe was upset about losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:13.16,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't seem very happy about winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.81,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I'd say that Haru was more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:20.07,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.28,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:25.42,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,That's great?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:30.86,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That was when
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:34.18,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,we were found by a teacher \Nwho heard all the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:36.22,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get why he'd say that after losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.99,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru just wanted to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:43.56,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,He's back to his old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:48.89,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru was never one to care about \Nwinning or improving his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:53.40,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Will my brother also go \Nback to his old self?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:05.02,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,You still need one more member, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:06.92,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:09.04,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me join!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:16.07,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only ones who \Ncan change my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:18.62,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,If you're willing to have me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:21.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can serve as your \Nmanager and help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.26,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, ooh. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:25.98,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Kou-chan offered to join the swim club!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.29,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:30.50,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That means the swim club is \Nofficially open for business!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:32.13,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.91,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's wonderful news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:40.12,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get to swim with everyone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:44.07,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we still have a \Nlot of prep work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:46.97,Main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,That's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:48.34,Main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:50.28,Main,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,You never finish your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:51.92,Main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I eat my ham!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:52.92,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.58,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:56.30,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You can have some of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:59.60,Main,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, I want some too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:00.81,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.81,0:18:01.97,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:04.81,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I believe the swimming \Nclub you used to go to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:07.49,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,is finally being torn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.48,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Hurts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:18.14,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,It's not easy to watch as \Nyour memories are destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:20.41,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Were you a part of this club?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.68,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can't go against the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:24.62,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:27.41,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:34.76,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Coach Sasabe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:37.19,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,It's Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.48,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.82,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,You got real big, Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:43.97,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,It's been too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:47.83,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I work part-time as \Na pizza deliveryman now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:50.62,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come here for one last glimpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:52.01,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:53.98,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd drop by on my \Nway back from a delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.49,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Are the other boys doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:59.77,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I go to the same \Nschool as Haru and Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.66,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still friends with Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:03.27,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:05.08,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,He goes to a different school though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:08.20,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Rin's back from Australia, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:12.67,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,He looked pretty glum when I last \Nsaw him, so I was a little worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:14.69,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Glum?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.59,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka didn't mention it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:20.72,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was during the winter of \Nyour first year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.72,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I was closing down the place for the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:26.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,end of the year when \NHaruka and Rin showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.81,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, they ran into each \Nother while Rin was back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.58,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Did they have a race?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:34.98,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. And Haruka won easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:38.79,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Rin was pretty upset about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:40.76,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Can't blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:43.24,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,He went to a swimming school abroad,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:45.01,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,and it didn't make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.28,Main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:56.17,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.42,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.63,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why Haru quit \Nswimming competitively.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:04.01,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he hurt Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:13.44,Nar/Thought/Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,The customer you have called \Nis currently unable to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:17.90,Nar/Thought/Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave your name and \Nmessage after the tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:21.08,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:22.71,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:26.93,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting up a swim club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:31.21,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,So you should join the swim team.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.33,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We might get to swim \Ntogether at a tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:37.93,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't need you to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:40.09,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I already decided to join the swim team.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:41.09,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:45.09,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doing this for a chance \Nto swim with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:49.64,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:52.52,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Here's to the establishment \Nof the new swim club!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:54.67,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:57.35,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,It's not warm enough to start swimming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:20:59.92,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,but we filled the pool as a test run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:03.20,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to toss these in together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.28,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.11,0:21:09.23,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,The swim club is finally ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:11.58,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can't get in the pool yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.71,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:14.21,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You were wearing your swimsuit again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:18.49,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get enough of those triceps!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:20.04,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,What? Triceps?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:23.64,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Haru, it's still too cold right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:24.80,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.09,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.29,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,He looks comfortable enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:28.77,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:30.49,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! His lips are turning purple!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:32.47,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the water \Nbefore you catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:34.70,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Haru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:36.37,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,No! He can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:37.86,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go find a net!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:39.44,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A net?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.32,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,So what's this Iwatobi-chan \NI've been hearing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:19.08,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's the mascot character for our town \Nthat was chosen from 987 entries last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.10,0:23:20.07,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I submitted an entry for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.07,0:23:21.28,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:23.97,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,So 1 of the 987 entries \Nwas from Haruka-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.97,0:23:24.89,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What was your entry?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.89,0:23:26.04,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.04,0:23:27.32,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Tobimaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.32,0:23:28.53,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,It's not cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:30.47,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Theoretical Dolphin Kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:36.02,NextEp,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(444,1)}Theoretical Dolphin Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:32.89,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,The swim club's about to get \Nan awesome new member!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:34.94,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Hooked by Iwatobi-chan?!
